reviewText: In this movie you will learn house architecture,festivals,plantations and much more!  I grew up with this travel series as A kid!

This tape is 58 minutes long and shows you how to grill using direct and indirect heat. The chefs are Susan Specer (Bayona), Emeril La Grasse (Emeril's), Michael Uddo (G & E Courtyard Grill and Jamie Shannon (Commander's Palace.) They show you step by step and give handy little tips for delicious recipes! Fun to watch and try!
